---
// TradeForce Plumbing — CLEAN WHITE/BLUE PROFESSIONAL THEME
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>TradeForce Plumbing — Demo | SiteGenius</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; color: #1e293b; background: #fff; }

    .demo-bar { background: #2563eb; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 10px; font-size: 13px; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 999; }
    .demo-bar a { color: #bfdbfe; font-weight: 700; }

    .hero { min-height: 100vh; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e40af 0%, #1d4ed8 40%, #2563eb 100%); display: flex; align-items: center; padding-top: 50px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
    .hero::after { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 120px; background: #fff; clip-path: polygon(0 40%, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%); }
    .hero-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr; gap: 48px; align-items: center; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 3.2rem; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; line-height: 1.2; }
    .hero p { margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.05rem; color: #bfdbfe; line-height: 1.7; }
    .hero-btns { display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-top: 28px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn-white { padding: 16px 32px; background: #fff; color: #1d4ed8; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: 700; transition: 0.3s; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    .btn-white:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); }
    .btn-ghost { padding: 16px 32px; border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: 700; transition: 0.3s; }
    .btn-ghost:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
    .hero-card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius: 24px; padding: 36px; color: #fff; }
    .hero-card h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .hero-card .check { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 10px 0; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .hero-card .check span { color: #86efac; }

    .services { padding: 100px 24px; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .services h2 { text-align: center; font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .services > p { text-align: center; color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 48px; }
    .services-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 24px; }
    .svc { background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px; transition: 0.3s; }
    .svc:hover { border-color: #2563eb; box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(37,99,235,0.08); transform: translateY(-4px); }
    .svc .icon { font-size: 2.4rem; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .svc h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .svc p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #64748b; line-height: 1.6; }

    .trust { background: #f1f5f9; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .trust-inner { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr); gap: 24px; text-align: center; }
    .trust h3 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: #1d4ed8; }
    .trust p { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #64748b; margin-top: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }

    .cta { background: #1d4ed8; padding: 80px 24px; text-align: center; color: #fff; }
    .cta h2 { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .cta p { opacity: 0.8; margin-bottom: 24px; }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero-card { display: none; }
      .hero h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
      .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .trust-inner { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="demo-bar">🔧 This is a demo site built by <a href="/">SiteGenius</a> — <a href="/get-a-quote">Get yours today</a></div>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div>
        <h1>Wellington's Most Trusted Plumber</h1>
        <p>Licensed, insured, and on time. From leaky taps to full bathroom renovations — we've got you covered, 24/7.</p>
        <div class="hero-btns">
          <a href="/get-a-quote" class="btn-white">Get a Free Quote</a>
          <a href="tel:0800123456" class="btn-ghost">📞 0800 123 456</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-card">
        <h3>Why Choose Us?</h3>
        <div class="check"><span>✓</span> Licensed & fully insured</div>
        <div class="check"><span>✓</span> 24/7 emergency callout</div>
        <div class="check"><span>✓</span> Free, no-obligation quotes</div>
        <div class="check"><span>✓</span> 100% satisfaction guarantee</div>
        <div class="check"><span>✓</span> Same-day service available</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="trust">
    <div class="trust-inner">
      <div><h3>15+</h3><p>Years Experience</p></div>
      <div><h3>2,500+</h3><p>Jobs Completed</p></div>
      <div><h3>4.9★</h3><p>Google Rating</p></div>
      <div><h3>1hr</h3><p>Avg Response</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="services">
    <h2>Our Services</h2>
    <p>Professional plumbing for homes and businesses across Wellington.</p>
    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="svc"><div class="icon">🚨</div><h3>Emergency Repairs</h3><p>Burst pipes, blocked drains, gas leaks — we respond fast, 24/7.</p></div>
      <div class="svc"><div class="icon">🛁</div><h3>Bathroom Renovations</h3><p>Complete bathroom design and installation to transform your space.</p></div>
      <div class="svc"><div class="icon">🔥</div><h3>Hot Water Systems</h3><p>Installation, repair, and maintenance of all hot water cylinder types.</p></div>
      <div class="svc"><div class="icon">🪠</div><h3>Blocked Drains</h3><p>CCTV inspection and high-pressure water jetting to clear any blockage.</p></div>
      <div class="svc"><div class="icon">⛽</div><h3>Gas Fitting</h3><p>Licensed gas fitters for safe installation and compliance work.</p></div>
      <div class="svc"><div class="icon">🔧</div><h3>Maintenance Plans</h3><p>Regular inspections to prevent costly emergency repairs.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <h2>Need a Plumber?</h2>
    <p>Call now for a free, no-obligation quote. Same-day service available.</p>
    <a href="/get-a-quote" class="btn-white">Get Free Quote →</a>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
